				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: The deep shard, vt key<a name="42867"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">May 28 04 9:15 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>I soloed it. But I got lucky, second mob I killed dropped it. <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-2.gif" border="0" alt="Big Smile" hspace="2" /> 
<br />

<br />
You'll need to get across the invisible bridge, and once you're across it, head left. The last tunnel on the left has 3 spawns of thought horrors at the entrance. They can be lulled, and I'm pretty sure they were mezzable. Pull a single, mezz, dispel (they are casters, so many of them have damageshields), slow and attack. Remember they run at low hp so have snare handy. Drop rate is best across the invis bridge. I wouldn't stray too far in the tunnels, just take it easy and don't take risks, CR in TD is a bish.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
